Your Own
Coaching Platform
How will having your own coaching platform help you impact more lives? It
frees up your time
to connect with your audience, work on your business, and do the stuff you truly enjoy.
Your own APP!  We will help you showcase your unique brand and training style while you retain ownership of all your own content and customer information.  No "powered by" branding.  No links to other competitive trainers.  Everything is 100% your brand. And you get paid every weekday as the sales come in.
You maintain full control over every plan your clients receive, except without the time consuming headaches of other 1:1 gym-based systems.  MacroActive was built by fitness creators to achieve impact at scale from day one.
VIP Coaching, your own mindset content, supplement guides, custom Spotify playlists to share with your fans, One-Click cross-selling your other offers all in-app (iOS/Android/WebApp), and the list goes on...
Enjoy a small army of fitness professionals dedicated to your customers, looking after each client so you don’t have to.  Finally be able to take a holiday!
